---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import ProjectCard from "../components/ProjectCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <NavBar />

  <div class="mainBody text-center">
    <div class="blog">
      <h1>Hi there!  I'm Anna</h1>
      <p>
        I love working with and learning about new technologies and programming
        languages, especially through open-source projects!  I do a little art
        on the side and I almost always have some sort of project going (whether
        or not itâ€™s listed here yet).
      </p>
      <p>
        When it comes to programming, I love solving problems.  Be it maintaining
        a project, or making something new.. it always draws me in; if there's a
        problem to be solved, you'll find me interested in working on it.  I do
        often have a preference for working with databases, the server side, or on
        standalone desktop applications; I essentially prefer backend development
        by definition (as evidenced by this website I'll still do frontend though).
      </p>
      <br />
      <h2>Find Me Online</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="text-left">
      <ProjectCard
        title="Codeberg"
        href=https://codeberg.org/Empress-Anna/
        description={`My Codeberg account, this is where I keep most of my repos
                      and the majority of my projects`}
        image_src="/logos/codeberg.svg"
      />
      <ProjectCard
        title="Github"
        href=https://github.com/Purple-Fox-Coder
        description={`My GitHub account, I mostly keep my older projects here,
                      however if the project calls for github specifically then
                      it will be here.  An example are my packages for the Pulsar
                      editor`}
        image_src="/logos/github.svg"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="blog">
      <!-- Site aside -->
      <br />
      <br />
      <p>
        Featured projects are listed on my <a href="../">homepage</a>
        or, you can look through all of my projects at
        <a href="../portfolio">my projects page</a>!
      </p>
      <p>
        If you find an issue with the website, feel free to
        <a href="https://github.com/Purple-Fox-Coder/plutonia.org/issues/new?template=bug_report.md">
          make a bug report on the GitHub
        </a>!  You can also view the source code at:
        <a href="https://github.com/Purple-Fox-Coder/plutonia.org">
          github.com/Purple-Fox-Coder/plutonia.org
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
